imdb.plot outline: Join host Melinda Keifer for WCTE's weekly series, Live Green Tennessee. We'll take you all over the state of Tennessee, talking with our local Farmers, Gardeners, and Neighbors about how our agricultural heritage and local wisdom can help all of us lead greener, more prosperous and healthy lives.

plot: We'll take you all over the state of Tennessee, talking with our local Farmers, Gardeners, and Neighbors about how our agricultural heritage and local wisdom can help all of us lead greener, more prosperous and healthy lives.

Join host Melinda Keifer for WCTE's weekly series, _Live Green Tennessee_ (qv). We'll take you all over the state of Tennessee, talking with our local Farmers, Gardeners, and Neighbors about how our agricultural heritage and local wisdom can help all of us lead greener, more prosperous and healthy lives.
